title: What causes Obesity in Kiribati
summary: This chart shows the percentages of What was the Cause of Obesity in Kiribati .
From the chart we see that approximately 24.3 percentage of the Cause for Obesity was from Fast_Food , whereas 35 percentage of the Cause came from Lack_of_Exercise of .
The highest percentage of the Cause of Obesity came from Genetic with 40.1 percentage .
gold: This chart indicates three possible causes of obesity in the Kiribati population . It indicates the main cause of obesity was attributed to genetic cause with 40 % of the sample identifying that as the main reason . Only 25 % indicated fast food contributed to the problem .
